		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello everybody,
<br />
<br />I have a non working Famicom Disk System. It is not the typical belt problem, it doesn't power on. I've tried using the power supply and batteries. Nothing. Then I suppose it's an electronic problem.
<br />
<br />I was looking for a schematics or a service manual and google brings to me to this amazing site...  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_surprised.gif" alt=":o" title="Surprised" /> 
<br />
<br />I'll apreciate if someone could tell me where to find some information to try to repair the FDS.
<br />
<br />Thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


