	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi,
<br />
<br />I know Famicom uses a 7805 voltage regulator. I attach an image of the Disk System regulator labeled B1009. Anybody knows if it is a 7805 also? Maybe a 7809?
<br />
<br /><img src="http://img41.imageshack.us/img41/7372/img7358p.jpg" alt="Image" />
<br />
<br />Thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


